{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":false,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"RemotePlayback.cancelWatchAvailability()","mdn_url":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/RemotePlayback/cancelWatchAvailability","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>The <strong><code>cancelWatchAvailability()</code></strong> method of the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/RemotePlayback\"><code>RemotePlayback</code></a> interface cancels the request to watch for one or all available devices.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js-nolint notranslate\">cancelWatchAvailability()\ncancelWatchAvailability(id)\n</pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parameters","title":"Parameters","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"id\"><code>id</code> <span class=\"badge inline optional\">Optional</span></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>The <code>callbackId</code> of a particular remote playback device.</p>\n    <p>If a <code>callbackId</code> of a specific device is passed in, then that device will be removed from the list of watched devices. Otherwise, the whole list will be cleared.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"return_value","title":"Return value","isH3":true,"content":"<p>A <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Promise\"><code>Promise</code></a> that resolves with <code>undefined</code>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"exceptions","title":"Exceptions","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"invalidstateerror\"><code>InvalidStateError</code> <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMException\"><code>DOMException</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Thrown if <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/disableRemotePlayback\" title=\"disableRemotePlayback\"><code>disableRemotePlayback</code></a> is <code>true</code> for the media element.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"notfounderror\